Milan are also interested in Allan Saint-Maximin, but a deal is difficult as Nice want at least &euro;30m and there is not a lot of time left in the transfer window, according to <br />
@DiMarzio<br />
<br />
<br />
Milan are trying to sign Carrasco, but it's not an easy deal. The main problem is to reach an agreement with Dalian Yifan with the president being in Spain. The contacts will continue during the night. The deal has not been unlocked yet, according to <br />
@DiMarzio<br />
<br />
Agent Federico Pastorello to Sky: &quot;Carrasco has been taken off the market by his club. Maybe talks will reopen in the summer.&quot;

